# ── Admin Access ──
# SECURITY: Admin access is granted via Appwrite user labels ONLY.
# To grant admin access:
# 1. Go to Appwrite Console → Authentication → Users
# 2. Select the user
# 3. Go to Labels tab
# 4. Add label: "admin"
# Email-based admin checks have been removed for security reasons.

